Czech Cabinet May Let Pension Funds Risk More, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 
2011-05-25T06:13:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/czech-cabinet-may-let-pension-funds-risk-more-hospodarske-says.html
The Czech government is preparing a
legislative change that would remove the obligation for pension
funds to compensate clients for eventual losses,  Hospodarske
Noviny  reported, citing Deputy Finance Minister Klara Krol.  The new legislation may allow funds to apply riskier
investment strategies, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
 placa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
